data.description: Unbelievable opportunity in this wonderful 3/1/1 rancher! Enter from the covered porch to the living room with gas fireplace and entertainment niche. Open to kitchen with counter bar seating and all appliances! Walkout Master with private entry to full bathroom could be a study or den! Washer /Dryer included in the laundry directly across from a linen closet. Backyard fully fenced with side gate and storage shed. Quick access to Ft Carson! Will not last!
